  "description": "[Description]",
  "readme_markdown": "<h2><a id=\"user-content-description\" class=\"anchor\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"#description\"><svg class=\"octicon octicon-link\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" version=\"1.1\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M7.775 3.275a.75.75 0 001.06 1.06l1.25-1.25a2 2 0 112.83 2.83l-2.5 2.5a2 2 0 01-2.83 0 .75.75 0 00-1.06 1.06 3.5 3.5 0 004.95 0l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 00-4.95-4.95l-1.25 1.25zm-4.69 9.64a2 2 0 010-2.83l2.5-2.5a2 2 0 012.83 0 .75.75 0 001.06-1.06 3.5 3.5 0 00-4.95 0l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 004.95 4.95l1.25-1.25a.75.75 0 00-1.06-1.06l-1.25 1.25a2 2 0 01-2.83 0z\"></path></svg></a>[Description]</h2>\n<p>Repair Damaged Items in your Hand Easily!</p>\n<p>You Can Set PaymentMode to XP or MOENY in Config!</p>\n<p>You Can Set CoolDown for Repairing Items in Config!</p>\n<h2><a id=\"user-content-usage\" class=\"anchor\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"#usage\"><svg class=\"octicon octicon-link\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" version=\"1.1\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M7.775 3.275a.75.75 0 001.06 1.06l1.25-1.25a2 2 0 112.83 2.83l-2.5 2.5a2 2 0 01-2.83 0 .75.75 0 00-1.06 1.06 3.5 3.5 0 004.95 0l2.5-2.5a3.5 3.5 0 00-4.95-4.95l-1.25 1.25zm-4.69 9.64a2 2 0 010-2.83l2.5-2.5a2 2 0 012.83 0 .75.75 0 001.06-1.06 3.5 3.5 0 00-4.95 0l-2.5 2.5a3.5 3.5 0 004.95 4.95l1.25-1.25a.75.75 0 00-1.06-1.06l-1.25 1.25a2 2 0 01-2.83 0z\"></path></svg></a>[Usage]</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Put phar from Poggit into <code>plugins</code> folder</li>\n<li>Edit the config.yml file of plugin in <code>plugin_data/EasyRepairItems</code></li>\n  <li>you can set <code>XP: false</code> to set PaymentMode to MONEY (for Players) </li>\n  <li>You Can Repair Your Damaged Item in Your Hand With Command:</li>\n<ul>\n<li>/repair\n  <ul>\n    <li>Permission (For Repair Without Money or Xp): EasyRepairItems.command</li>\n    <li>Default: Op</li>\n  </ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<p>I hope you enjoy using this plugin.<p>\n<h2>[Libraries]</h2>\n<il>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/onebone/EconomyS/tree/3.x/EconomyAPI/\">EconomyAPI</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>",
